results.deck: It's a part of Activision, except, you know, they only put out games that will make you cry!!
results.description: Activision Value Publishing, Inc. is an American computer and video game company, a merger of Activision, Expert Software and Head Games Publishing. They were the initial publishers of Big Rigs: Over the Road Racing, a game that is considered to be one of the worst games ever made.
